{"tid":887704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[none care]露宿漢猝死大埔墟巴士總站","createTime":"2018-11-03T06:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T04:34:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd89f5c3f7943083a9a1c77002e779b1f927921e","tid":887704,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"大埔南運路9號大埔墟巴士總站，今早(3日)7時59分，一名年近70歲在站內露宿的男子，被兩名到訪友人發現昏迷不醒，大驚下立即報警。救護員到場，證實男子已氣絕死亡。據友人向警方稱，死者剛於一個多月前到上址露宿，有哮喘病紀錄，警方調查後，相信案件無可疑，正聯絡其家人助查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181103/bkn-20181103092248316-1103_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181103%2Fbkn-20181103092248316-1103_00822_001.html&d=sEvC7CgUb9oZl4rpuPTWY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9016f490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181103/bkn-20181103092248316-1103_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"83afcef20992e1a24f2430ce517be4eb8c409c08","tid":887704,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181103/photo/bkn-20181103092248316-1103_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181103115426\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181103%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181103092248316-1103_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181103115426&h=e211f559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n露宿漢倒斃帆布帳篷內，兩名友人協助警方調查。"},{"pid":"998b58bd62d51127b34bc4c1316482d11a211d22","tid":887704,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪娶大陸婆嗰啲阿伯"}]}